OL,3,CMan from Nottingham blames health
OL,4,Cservices for his brother's death
OL,6,FPeter Bearne has been speaking to Adam
OL,7,FHussain's brother, Qasim
OL,9,FA coroner has concluded that health
OL,10,Fprofessionals missed "many
OL,11,Fopportunities" to spot that a young
OL,12,Fman from Nottingham had a life-
OL,13,Fthreatening illness in the days before
OL,14,Fhe died.
OL,16,FAdam Hussain, from Clifton, was
OL,17,Finitially sent to the hospital,
OL,18,Fassessed, and then discharged.
