OL,3,CMan from Nottingham blames health
OL,4,Cservices for his brother's death
OL,6,F"I definitely thought things weren't
OL,7,Fright. But when we tried to reach out
OL,8,Ffor help there was no urgency and I
OL,9,Ffeel the emergency services, they kind
OL,10,Fof pushed everything to the side."
OL,12,FDuring the inquest, Qasim had to hear
OL,13,Fthe desperate 999 call his brother
OL,14,Fmade two days before his death. His
OL,15,Fvoice was barely audible, his body
OL,16,Fracked with pain. He wasn't sent an
OL,17,Fambulance.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G4/7
