OL,3,CMan from Nottingham blames health
OL,4,Cservices for his brother's death
OL,6,FQasim said, "I think the decisions
OL,7,Fthat were made were quite
OL,8,Foutrageous...I think there were many
OL,9,Fchances of him being saved."
OL,11,FQasim says the loss of his brother has
OL,12,Fleft him heartbroken. He's set up a
OL,13,Ffundraiser in his brother's memory to
OL,14,Fhelp build wells in parts of Pakistan
OL,15,Fwhere water is scarce.
