OL,3,CMan from Nottingham blames health
OL,4,Cservices for his brother's death
OL,6,FOn the same day, the coroner also
OL,7,Ffound that another man, Jake
OL,8,FCartwright, died in January in similar
OL,9,Fcircumstances, where sepsis was not
OL,10,Fdetected, and an ambulance was not
OL,11,Fsent.
OL,13,FThe coroner criticised both the East
OL,14,FMidlands Ambulance Service and NEMS,
OL,15,Fwho assess people who call 111.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G6/7
