OL,3,CMan from Nottingham blames health
OL,4,Cservices for his brother's death
OL,6,FDr Steven Dykes, Clinical Director of
OL,7,FEast Midlands Ambulance Service, "A
OL,8,Fhuge apology to you that the system
OL,9,Ffailed you at a time of need .... I
OL,10,Fwill work to make sure this doesn't
OL,11,Fhappen again."
OL,13,FDr Nita Mandhar, Medical Director of
OL,14,Fthe NEMS, said, "I want to express
OL,15,Fthat we do care. Our intention is
OL,16,Falways to do our very best. Jake and
OL,17,FAdam will remain at the heart of our
OL,18,Freflections and actions."
